  * - $$title$$, $$value$$, $$open$$, $$high$$, $$low$$, $$close$$
  * - $$volume$$, $$time$$
  * - $$upper$$, $$middle$$, $$lower$$ (for bands)
  * - Custom placeholders from customData
  ```

